    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >糟了，看来你的送货自行车被偷了。别担心，你还有一辆备用的独轮车可以使用。穿越繁忙的城市街道，确保你的送货准时到达。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/d2e2a918b20e791c32faec6f1570ce9d.webp?t=1755277236\" width=600 height=50 /></span>你将不得不在这个复杂的城市景观中穿行。到底是哪位建筑师允许设计了这个地方!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/09b11c97d8aa3d4ee69543bba971c648.poster.avif?t=1755277236\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/09b11c97d8aa3d4ee69543bba971c648.webm?t=1755277236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/09b11c97d8aa3d4ee69543bba971c648.mp4?t=1755277236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/bd8ff261b96053eb27fb474522778ccb.webp?t=1755277236\" width=600 height=50 /></span>与 1-4 名送货员一起送披萨，并彼此竞争。毕竟，第一个送到的人会得到最多的小费……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/22a12e07d731af07252c626f16646009.poster.avif?t=1755277236\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/22a12e07d731af07252c626f16646009.webm?t=1755277236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138570/extras/22a12e07d731af07252c626f16646009.mp4?t=1755277236\" type=\"video/mp4\">